| cname    | sname   |
+----------+---------+
| Giovanni | AxelRod |
| Pereira  | Motika  |
| Hoffman  | Peel    |
| Clemens  | Peel    |
| Cisneros | Rifkin  |
| Grass    | Serres  |
| Liu      | Serres  |
+----------+---------+


