Q46: Write a query that will give you all orders for more than $1000.00.
Ans: SELECT * FROM orders WHERE amt>1000;

output:
+------+---------+------------+------+------+
| ONUM | AMT     | ODATE      | CNUM | SNUM |
+------+---------+------------+------+------+
